{"tid":2116310,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方粉嶺坪輋倉庫檢值4300萬 重67.3公斤懷疑冰毒　拘兩漢","createTime":"2020-07-20T05:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T16:32:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":70,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"f54d123c15a28e594ea9c4bc7238fdd6fbfef73b","tid":2116310,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538799-20200720.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538799-20200720.htm&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zaC2H8C9v%2BSdTXBEGJsevNE%3D&h=47b786f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1538799-20200720.htm&h=e5a9d664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1538799-20200720.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n警方前日根據線報，突擊搜查粉嶺坪輋孔嶺西村一個倉庫，檢獲重67.3公斤的懷疑冰毒，市值約4300萬元，拘捕兩名本地人士。<br />\n<br />\n毒品調查科警司鄒旺忠表示，經調查後，發現這批懷疑毒品是以船運方式，由墨西哥運入本港。他說，在疫情下，毒販經出入境管制站帶毒品到香港有困難，冰毒價格自封關後上升兩成，相信毒販會利用一切方式偷運毒品到香港。"},{"pid":"bc330988ddfb71a3e96ce13dbd91ae75e5265142","tid":2116310,"uid":244818,"like":76,"dislike":1,"score":75,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:37:15.000Z","msg":"私落冰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},{"pid":"f3d1a2e8546ecce465d6db677af209bff56bdf6e","tid":2116310,"uid":48579,"like":122,"dislike":1,"score":121,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:37:16.000Z","msg":"狗隊要入貨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9cf1653b9944a83604d038ceecfc90c4cc0427","tid":2116310,"uid":246118,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T05:37:19.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agre